GuruCue,is,a,service,that,helps,users,choose,what,to,watch,by,giving,them,a,visual,cue,when,choosing,a,movie,or,video,according,to,their,taste,The,service,is,intended,for,any,provider,of,movie,or,video,content,looking,to,improve,the,personalization,of,their,services,for,their,end,users,Users,rate,movies,they,have,watched,and,the,more,movies,they,have,rated,the,better,the,recommendations,that,are,given,The,API,is,currently,in,beta,Interested,developers,should,contact,the,provider,at,http,www,gurucue,com,feedback,php,to,request,permission,to,test,the,API